snippet: A 16-year-old student who previously threatened to go on a shooting rampage at his school stabbed three students and a janitor on Thursday in Oulu, the police said.
abstract: Sixteen-year-old student who threatened earlier in 2013 to go on shooting rampage at his vocational school in northern Finland stabs three students and janitor; all four victims are reported in stable condition.
lead_paragraph: A 16-year-old student who previously threatened to go on a shooting rampage at his school stabbed three students and a janitor on Thursday in Oulu, the police said.
